o\": 1513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Philippines' only Woman Grandmaster, Frayna emerged as the best scorer with 8 points out of 11 games, while Mendoza tallied 5.5 out of 10 while manning the top board.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1702, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1536, \"end\": 1547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9999999972260412, \"rank\": 2.72545069630523e-09, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 1554, \"end\": 1571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIDE_titles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.997575773350336e-51, \"text\": \"Woman Grandmaster\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIDE_titles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIDE_titles\"}, {\"begin\": 1644, \"end\": 1651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mendoza_Province\", \"score\": 0.991035005744206, \"rank\": 0.009046092420461175, \"text\": \"Mendoza\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mendoza_Province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mendoza_Province\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Frayna\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"the best scorer\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"8 points\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"11 games\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1636}, {\"ngram\": \"the top board\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fronda totaled 6.5 points out of 10 games, Canino scored 6 points out of eight, while Bernadette Galas gained 3 points out of five.\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1747, \"end\": 1753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canino\", \"score\": 0.9999999998808562, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canino\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canino\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canino\"}, {\"